    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='156:182'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '008-1a' );" name="008-1a" class="pb">[008-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='182:190'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='190:200'>　三家詩拾遺卷八</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='200:221'>　　　　　　　　　　柳州府知府范家相撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='221:226'>　小雅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='226:231'>節南山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='231:254'>　董仲舒曰周室之衰其卿大夫緩於義而急於利無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='254:277'>　推讓之風而有争田之訟故詩人疾而刺之　韋昭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='277:288'>　曰節南山平王時作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='288:314'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '008-1b' );" name="008-1b" class="pb">[008-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='314:337'>　　按四章瑣瑣姻婭則無膴仕豈江都所云無推讓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='337:360'>　　之風耶若争田之訟如下篇皇父徹我牆屋田卒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='360:382'>　　汚萊大雅瞻卬所云人有土田汝覆奪之是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='382:409'>節彼南山　憂心如惔<span class='krp-note'>韓作炎說/文作㶣同</span>　何用不監</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='409:425'>　韓傳節視也監領也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='425:435'>昊天不慵降此鞠凶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='435:462'>　韓傳慵作庸易也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span>　薛君曰萬人顒顒仰天告愬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='462:471'>　<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='471:497'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '008-2a' );" name="008-2a" class="pb">[008-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='497:520'>　　以庸為易言天之降訩必俟其惡稔而降不易降</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='520:525'>　　也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='525:537'>四牡項領　蹙蹙靡所騁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='537:560'>　魯詩劉向曰久駕而長不得行項領不亦宜乎易曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='560:579'>　臀旡膚其行次且此之謂也<span class='krp-note'>新/序</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='579:596'>　韓詩薛君曰騁馳也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='596:619'>　　鄭氏以四牡為人君所駕今但養大其領而不為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='619:642'>　　用喻大臣自恣不為王用與劉說同非奔走勞敝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='642:668'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '008-2b' );" name="008-2b" class="pb">[008-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='668:674'>　　之狀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='674:678'>正月</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='678:693'>正月繁霜　民之訛言亦孔之將</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='693:716'>　魯詩霜降失節不以其時　民之訛言亦孔之將言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='716:737'>　民以是為非甚衆大也<span class='krp-note'>俱劉向/政事疏</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='737:752'>瞻彼中林侯薪侯蒸　視天夢夢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='752:779'>　韓傳夢夢惡貌<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span>　外傳曰瞻彼中林侯薪侯蒸言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='779:788'>　朝廷皆小人也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='788:814'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '008-3a' );" name="008-3a" class="pb">[008-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='814:824'>維號斯言有倫有脊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='824:847'>　董仲舒曰物莫不有凡號號莫不有散名事各順於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='847:870'>　名名各順於天天人之際合而為一謂之德道詩曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='870:885'>　維號斯言有倫有脊此之謂也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='885:908'>　　以號為名嫉邪思正其義亦長蓋名不正則言不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='908:931'>　　順事不成至於民無所措手足為害大矣幽王寵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='931:956'>　　妾為妻訛言以是為非名之不正莫斯為甚是可哀也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='956:978'>夭夭是㭬<span class='krp-note'>夭夭蔡邕作天夭/㭬作加韓作㧻</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='978:1004'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '008-3b' );" name="008-3b" class="pb">[008-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1004:1024'>　張衡曰速速方穀天夭亦加<span class='krp-note'>夭通/妖</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1024:1030'>十月之交</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1030:1052'>　齊詩翼奉曰竊讀齊詩聞五際之要十月之交篇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1052:1079'>　梅福曰杜亡秦之路數御十月之交<span class='krp-note'>本/傳</span>　孟康曰十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1079:1091'>　月之交刺后族太盛也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1091:1115'>　魯詩鄭氏曰此為厲王之詩經師移易其次第耳幽王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1115:1138'>　時司徒乃鄭桓公友非此篇所云番也<span class='krp-note'>詩/譜</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1138:1161'>　　顔師古述魯詩作厲王詩知鄭所云亦本魯詩並</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1161:1187'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '008-4a' );" name="008-4a" class="pb">[008-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1187:1209'>　　緯書之說　按中樞擿雒貳曰昌受符厲借嬖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1209:1232'>　　十之世權在相又曰剡者配姬以放賢山崩川潰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1232:1255'>　　納小人家伯異哉震推度灾曰十月之交氣之相</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1255:1278'>　　交周之十月夏之八月日及其食也君弱臣強故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1278:1301'>　　天垂象以其徵辛者正秋之王氣卯者正春之臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1301:1324'>　　位日為君辰為臣八月之日交卯食辛矣辛之為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1324:1347'>　　君幼弱而不明卯之為臣秉權而為政故辛之言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1347:1370'>　　新隂氣盛而陽微生其君細弱而任卯臣也以上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1370:1396'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '008-4b' );" name="008-4b" class="pb">[008-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1396:1419'>　　緯書皆指厲王夫國語明載幽之三年西周三川</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1419:1442'>　　皆震所謂山冡崒崩也是年三川竭所謂高岸為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1442:1465'>　　谷深谷為陵也王基杜預以長厯推之斷其非厲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1465:1474'>　　王之詩甚明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1474:1492'>彼月而食則維其常此日而食于何不臧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1492:1515'>　魯訓厲王無道内嬖熾盛政化失理故致灾異日為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1515:1537'>　之食為不善也<span class='krp-note'>谷永傳顔師/古𫐠魯訓</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1537:1560'>　韓詩内傳月食非常也比之日猶常也日食則不臧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1560:1586'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '008-5a' );" name="008-5a" class="pb">[008-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1586:1601'>　矣<span class='krp-note'>漢書天文/志注引傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1601:1624'>　　按魯詩如鄭氏自此篇至小宛皆厲王詩而韓詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1624:1629'>　　異</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1629:1655'>皇父卿士番維司徒　艷妻煽方處<span class='krp-note'>魯作閻妻/煽方熾</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1655:1691'>　魯詩閻妻驕煽日以不臧<span class='krp-note'>顔師古注閻妻嬖寵之族/也皇父卿士番維司徒皆</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1691:1715'>　<span class='krp-note'>以刺厲王滛於色故皇/父之属因嬖寵而為官</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1715:1738'>　　按谷永疏又有抑褒閻之亂語或魯詩别有可証</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1738:1749'>　　歟艷緯書又作剡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1749:1775'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '008-5b' );" name="008-5b" class="pb">[008-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1775:1802'>抑此皇父　不憗遺一老　韓傳抑意也<span class='krp-note'>意音/噫</span>憗誾也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1802:1810'>　<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1810:1815'>雨無正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1815:1838'>　劉安世曰少讀韓詩雨無極篇序曰雨無極大夫刺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1838:1861'>　幽王也首有雨無其極傷我稼穡八字<span class='krp-note'>集/傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1861:1894'>淪胥以鋪<span class='krp-note'>韓作熏胥以痡又作熏魯齊韓/皆作熏顔師古曰謂相熏蒸也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1894:1917'>　韓傳熏帥也胥相也痡病也言此無罪之人而使有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1917:1938'>　罪者相帥而病之是其太甚也<span class='krp-note'>漢書/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1938:1964'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '008-6a' );" name="008-6a" class="pb">[008-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1964:1968'>小旻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1968:1997'>謀猶回遹<span class='krp-note'>韓作/泬</span>　韓詩薛君曰回泬邪僻也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1997:2038'>[言*翕][言*翕]訿訿<span class='krp-note'>韓[言*翕]/作潝</span>　韓傳不善之貌<span class='krp-note'>爾雅不/供職也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2038:2064'>民雖靡膴<span class='krp-note'>韓作/腜</span>　韓傳靡腜猶無幾何<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2064:2085'>　　王肅膴讀作幠大也言無大有人也意同韓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2085:2089'>小宛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2089:2114'>翰飛戾天<span class='krp-note'>韓戾/作厲</span>　韓詩厲疾也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2114:2124'>哀我填寡宜岸宜獄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2124:2150'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '008-6b' );" name="008-6b" class="pb">[008-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2150:2175'>　韓傳填作疹苦也鄉亭之繫曰岸朝廷曰獄<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2175:2179'>小弁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2179:2202'>　趙岐曰小弁伯竒之詩也伯竒仁人而父虐之故作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2202:2228'>　小弁之詩曰何辜于天親親而悲怨之詞也<span class='krp-note'>孟子/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2228:2249'>　　孫疏謂伯竒當是宜臼然魯詩原作伯竒也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2249:2276'>　魯詩王充曰伯竒放流首髪早白故曰維憂用老<span class='krp-note'>論/衡</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2276:2299'>　蔡邕曰伯竒既逐履霜以足採葶花以食其隣大夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2299:2313'>　閔之乃賦小弁<span class='krp-note'>琴/操</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2313:2339'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '008-7a' );" name="008-7a" class="pb">[008-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2339:2362'>　　按如琴操亦是賦小弁而非作也王充之說何以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2362:2367'>　　云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2367:2387'>疢如疾首　韓傳疢作疛心疾也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2387:2397'>有漼者淵萑葦淠淠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2397:2419'>　韓外傳有漼者淵萑葦淠淠言大者無所不容也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2419:2435'>　　意以淵喻父母以萑葦自比也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2435:2439'>巧言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2439:2458'>僭始既涵　韓傳涵作減少也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2458:2484'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '008-7b' );" name="008-7b" class="pb">[008-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2484:2500'>匪其止共<span class='krp-note'>韓作/恭</span>維王之卭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2500:2524'>　魯詩劉向曰此傷奸臣蔽主以為樂者也<span class='krp-note'>説/苑</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2524:2545'>　韓外傳匪其止恭言不恭其職事而病其王也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2545:2555'>躍躍毚兔遇犬獲之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2555:2579'>　韓傳作趯趯往來之貌獲得也言趯趯之毚兔數往</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2579:2602'>　來逃匿其跡有時遇犬獲之<span class='krp-note'>司馬彪/史記注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2602:2607'>何人斯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2607:2626'>我心易也　韓傳易作施善也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2626:2652'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '008-8a' );" name="008-8a" class="pb">[008-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2652:2671'>伯氏吹塤仲氏吹篪　出此三物以詛爾斯</span><br/>
