<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4567:4590'>　韓詩衛武公飲酒悔過也言賔初就筵之時賔主秩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4590:4615'>　秩然俱敬也賔既醉止不知其為惡也<span class='krp-note'>後漢/書注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4615:4642'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '008-13b' );" name="008-13b" class="pb">[008-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='4642:4665'>　　朱子以是詩與抑戒相似必武公自悔之作當從</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='4665:4688'>　　韓義然詩曰大侯旣抗曰烝衎烈祖明是天子燕</span><br/>
