<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='4758:4778'>魚藻　有頒其首　韓傳頒衆貌<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='4778:4801'>　　魚之在藻衆首向上猶臣侍君飲莫不仰首向上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='4801:4820'>　　視君也下章有莘其尾則燕畢而散矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='4820:4847'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '008-14a' );" name="008-14a" class="pb">[008-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
