<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='5021:5040'>民之無良相怨一方受爵不讓至于已斯亡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='5040:5063'>　韓傳良善也言王者所為無有善者各相與於一方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='5063:5090'>　而怨之<span class='krp-note'>漢書/注</span>　外傳民皆居一方而怨其上不亡者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='5090:5113'>　未之有也受爵不讓至于巳斯亡言能知於人而不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='5113:5120'>　能自知也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='5120:5156'>如食宜<span class='krp-note'>韓作/儀</span>饇雨雪瀌瀌<span class='krp-note'>韓作/麃麃</span>見晛曰消<span class='krp-note'>韓作曣/晛聿消</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='5156:5174'>　韓傳儀我也曣晛日出也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='5174:5197'>　魯詩劉向曰君子道消則政日亂故為否小人道消</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='5197:5224'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '008-15a' );" name="008-15a" class="pb">[008-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='5224:5247'>　則政日治故為泰詩曰雨雪瀌瀌見晛曰消與易同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='5247:5256'>　義<span class='krp-note'>封/事</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='5256:5279'>都人士　孔頴達曰首章毛氏有之三家則亡今韓詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='5279:5302'>　實無首章　按春秋襄十二年傳引此行歸于周二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='5302:5325'>　句服䖍曰逸詩也蓋據三家詩言之也禮記緇衣長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='5325:5348'>　民者衣服不貳節全引首章則三家失之矣　緇衣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='5348:5371'>　引此乃美其君子而思念之詞毛傳引之以為傷今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='5371:5378'>　思古之詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='5378:5405'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '008-15b' );" name="008-15b" class="pb">[008-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='5405:5424'>黍苗　韋昭曰道召伯𫐠職勞來諸侯也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='5424:5442'>我任我輦我車我牛我行旣集蓋云歸哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='5442:5465'>　荀子曰仁人在上百姓貴之如帝親之如父母為之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='5465:5481'>　出死斷亡而愉者無他焉詩云云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='5481:5485'>白華</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='5485:5508'>英英<span class='krp-note'>韓作/泱泱</span>白雲念子懆懆<span class='krp-note'>韓作/㤄</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='5508:5529'>　韓傳泱泱雲貌㤄㤄意不悅好也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='5529:5533'>緜蠻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='5533:5560'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '008-16a' );" name="008-16a" class="pb">[008-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='5560:5578'>　韓詩薛君曰緜蠻文貌<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='5578:5588'>飲之食之教之誨之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='5588:5606'>　董仲舒曰先飲食而後教誨言治人也</span><br/>
